      tooltip: "Constants [CONSTANT] — Physical and mathematical constants as Abstract GTs. Unforgeable, incorruptible identity tokens for PI, E, PHI, c, h, k_B, N_A, G." },
    { offset: 13, name: "Stack", type: "Abstraction",
