B NE fault

TPERM 0 S         ; Additional permission
B NE fault

; === DATA VALIDATION ===
CMP 0 0           ; Non-negative?
B MI fault

CMP 0 1           ; Within max?
B GT fault

; === ALL PASSED - PROCEED ===
